      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for a budget-friendly option. While the engine starts and runs consistently, you might notice some minor vibrations at highway speeds and a slow leak in the power steering fluid. The interior shows visible signs of wear, including some fading on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Externally, there are several small dings and some paint oxidation on the hood, but it remains a solid, roadworthy car for its age.",
