    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously serviced and consistently stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade motorcar.",
      "price": 46500.0,
