    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is seriously in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken such good care of it, and it is a total dream to drive. If you are looking for a ride that is practically perfect in every way, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
