    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and a documented rear subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivers tactile engagement, complemented by a refreshed Sachs clutch and a limited-slip variable M differential. The chassis is dialed with Bilstein dampers and OE-spec bushings, maintaining factory kinematics. The paint remains original with zero evidence of oxidation, and the interior is free of bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. A mechanically pristine, turn-key example for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
